#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:217 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:242
#: data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:271 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:298
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:166 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:195
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:222 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:171
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:200
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:227
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:192
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:221
