#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:303 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:331
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:242 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:270
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:296
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Also, damaged land units which stay in town for one full turn without moving "
"are completely restored."
