#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:186 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:267
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:191 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:196
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:217 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:266
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a Barracks II, each new land unit built in a city will automatically "
"have Veteran status, which means that its attack and defense strengths are "
