#: data/civ2civ3/terrain.ruleset:259 data/classic/terrain.ruleset:252
#: data/experimental/terrain.ruleset:254 data/multiplayer/terrain.ruleset:252
#: data/royale/terrain.ruleset:259 data/sandbox/terrain.ruleset:260
msgid "No unit can enter this terrain, nor can any city work its tiles."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/terrain.ruleset:264 data/classic/terrain.ruleset:257
